Class SocketAdapter

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IsTechnologyAdapter, IComponent, IEndOfDayPerformer, IExceptionListener, IFIXListener, IFIXMessageProcessor, IFIXSource, IHasAttributes, IConfigurable, IRegisterable, IMessageListener, IMessageProcessor, IMessageSource, ICatalysEventListener, Cloneable, EventListener

    public class SocketAdapter
extends FIXSourceListenerBase
implements IsTechnologyAdapter
    This is a socket adapter that supports a 1-many relationship between a socket client and FIX sessions. The socket client communicates via a single port, which is managed by a SharedSocketAdapter.

    This message processor sets the storeMessages attribute to false to enable message reuse.
